ComicInfo.Summary: OverviewBack from the past, troubles a'brewin' for the FemForce. In order for She-Cat to hold in check the power of the evil cat -diety that possesses her, she must form a psychic bond with another being. For decades, that bond was with Joan Wayne. But Joan Wayne and Ms. Victory no longer exist (thanks to a forced overdose of the compound that gives Ms. Victory her powers). Only the unstable and antisocial Rad exists in Joan's place. Now that his relationship with She-Cat is gone, she's free to do what she wants, as she wants. She intends to disband the FemForce. Guest starring Tom Kelly, Stella Stargaze, and introducing Colt as new leader of the FemForce. "Breakables", written by Wes Covington, with pencils by Dell Barras, and inks by Danny Taverna.
